data.title: Sacred Heart Catholic Church Detail (Wilburton, Oklahoma)
data.meta_description:
Built in 1912 and located at 102 Center Point Road, this church was placed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1980.
	
	Wilburton is a small community located in southeastern Oklahoma between McAlester and Poteau. It is the county seat of Latimer County and home to Eastern Oklahoma State College.
